Modal_main_5830611\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qqn1705401956029.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qqn1705401956029.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qqn1705401956029.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ahx1665702844957\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n           \n ProcScript for Managing Components\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Component-based development enables you to create multi-tier applications. There are various ProcScript instructions and functions for handling component-based processing.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12218e1_d12219e1_d12220e1\">ProcScript instructions can:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__li_d5654e1_d5655e1_d5656e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12221e1_d12222e1_d12223e1\">Create new instances of components</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__li_d5657e1_d5658e1_d5659e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12224e1_d12225e1_d12226e1\">Delete instances of components</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__li_d5660e1_d5661e1_d5662e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12227e1_d12228e1_d12229e1\">Identify which instances of a component are attached to the current component instance</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__li_d5663e1_d5664e1_d5665e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12230e1_d12231e1_d12232e1\">Identify which instance of a component activated the current component instance</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__li_d5666e1_d5667e1_d5668e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12233e1_d12234e1_d12235e1\">Return the component type of any given component instance</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__li_d5669e1_d5670e1_d5671e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12236e1_d12237e1_d12238e1\">Send synchronous and asynchronous messages to an instance of a component</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__li_d5672e1_d5673e1_d5674e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12239e1_d12240e1_d12241e1\">Pass parameters to an instance of a component</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__li_d5675e1_d5676e1_d5677e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12242e1_d12243e1_d12244e1\">Activate operations in other components</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__p_d12245e1_d12246e1_d12247e1\">Services, reports, and server pages can exist and be activated anywhere in the deployment infrastructure. Forms must be processed on the system where they are displayed,</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">ProcScript for Component-Based Development</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">ProcScript command</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ryt1665702577808.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" title=\"Creates a new instance of a component.\">newinstance</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Deletes an instance of a component.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fxx1665702529732.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fxx1665702529732.html\" title=\"Calls an operation on a component instance.\">activate</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Starts an operation on a specified component.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xoj1719399495189.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xoj1719399495189.html\" title=\"Deletes an instance of a component.\">deleteinstance</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Deletes an instance of a component.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ndl1665702597453.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ndl1665702597453.html\" title=\"Return the name of the component from which the specified instance was created.\">$componentname</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return the name of the component from which the specified instance was created.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oqp1665702597552.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oqp1665702597552.html\" title=\"Return the type of the specified component instance.\">$componenttype</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return the type of the specified component instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bgv1665702597635.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bgv1665702597635.html\" title=\"Return a list of component instances attached to a specified component instance.\">$instancechildren</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return a list of instances attached to an instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dmr1665702598068.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmr1665702598068.html\" title=\"Return an indication whether data in the current instance has been retrieved from a database.\">$instancedb</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return an indication whether data in the current instance has been retrieved from a database.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"len1665702601301.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/len1665702601301.html\" title=\"Return the modification status of database fields in the current component instance.\">$instancedbmod</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return the modification status of database fields in the current component instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ccz1665702701341.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ccz1665702701341.html\" title=\"Return the handle of the requested component instance.\">$instancehandle</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return the handle of the requested instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"atw1665702600492.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/atw1665702600492.html\" title=\"Return or set the modification status of data in the current component instance.\">$instancemod</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return the modification status of data in the current component instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ksm1665702577277.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ksm1665702577277.html\" title=\"Return the name of the current component instance.\">$instancename</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return the name of the current component instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bgv1665702597635.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bgv1665702597635.html\" title=\"Return a list of component instances attached to a specified component instance.\">$instancechildren</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return a list of instances attached to an instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"itv1719677836442.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/itv1719677836442.html\" title=\"Return the name of the parent instance of the specified component instance.\">$instanceparent</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ahx1665702844957__table_d1271e1_d1272e1_d1273e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Return the name of the parent instance of the requested instance.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ezv1705470008998.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Component Memory Management</a><p>At runtime, component instances require memory to handle the component definition and component data. This memory is not necessarily freed when the component instance is deleted.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5830611\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5830611\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ProcScript for Managing Components Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ProcScript for Managing Components Component-based development enables you to create multi-tier applications. There are various ProcScript instructions and functions for handling component-based processing. ProcScript instructions can: Create new instances of components Delete instances of components Identify which instances of a component are attached to the current component instance Identify which instance of a component activated the current component instance Return the component type of any given component instance Send synchronous and asynchronous messages to an instance of a component Pass parameters to an instance of a component Activate operations in other components Services, reports, and server pages can exist and be activated anywhere in the deployment infrastructure. Forms must be processed on the system where they are displayed, Table 1. ProcScript for Component-Based Development ProcScript command Description newinstance Deletes an instance of a component. activate Starts an operation on a specified component. deleteinstance Deletes an instance of a component. $componentname Return the name of the component from which the specified instance was created. $componenttype Return the type of the specified component instance. $instancechildren Return a list of instances attached to an instance. $instancedb Return an indication whether data in the current instance has been retrieved from a database. $instancedbmod Return the modification status of database fields in the current component instance. $instancehandle Return the handle of the requested instance. $instancemod Return the modification status of data in the current component instance. $instancename Return the name of the current component instance. $instancechildren Return a list of instances attached to an instance. $instanceparent Return the name of the parent instance of the requested instance. Related Links Component Memory Management At runtime, component instances require memory to handle the component definition and component data. This memory is not necessarily freed when the component instance is deleted. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}